API README v1

Controllers expect all non-id fields found in the entities (found in /models)
Unless otherwise noted, POST = Create, PUT = Update, DELETE = Delete

# User 
Get user object by ID
GET		/users/:id

POST	/users/add			
PUT		/users/update/:id	
DELETE	/users/delete/:id	


# ClimateService
Get by Name
GET		/climate/getClimateService/:name/json		

Get All Climate service 
GET		/climate/getAllClimateServices/json			

POST	/climate/addClimateService					
PUT		/climate/updateClimateService/id/:id		
PUT		/climate/updateClimateService/name/:oldName	
DELETE	/climate/deleteClimateService/:id			

# Service Configuration
Get by ID
GET		/climate/getServiceConfiguration/:id/json 						
Get all service configurations created by a certain user
GET		/climate/getAllServiceConfigurationsByUserId/:userId/json		

POST	/climate/addServiceConfiguration								
PUT		/climate/updateServiceConfiguration/id/:id						
DELETE	/climate/deleteServiceConfiguration/:id							

# Parameter
Get All parameters
GET		/parameter/getAllParameters/json			
Get single Parameter by Name
GET		/parameter/getParameter/name/:name/json		
Get by ID
GET		/parameter/getParameter/id/:id/json			
POST	/parameter/addParameter						
PUT		/parameter/updateParameter/id/:id			
PUT		/parameter/updateParameter/name/:oldName	
DELETE  /parameter/deleteParameter/name/:name		

# ParameterOption
Get all parameter options
GET		/parameterOption/getAllParameterOptions/json		
Get single parameter option by id
GET		/parameterOption/getParameterOption/id/:id/json		
POST	/parameterOption/addParameterOption					
PUT		/parameterOption/updateParameterOption/id/:id		
DELETE	/parameterOption/deleteParameterOption/id/:id		

# JournalPublication
Get All
GET		/journalPublication/getAllJournalPublications/json		
Get By ID
GET		/journalPublication/getJournalPublication/id/:id/json	
POST	/journalPublication/addJournalPublication				
PUT		/journalPublication/updateJournalPublication/id/:id		
DELETE	/journalPublication/deleteJournalPublication/id/:id		

