# Service Configuration Item
GET		/climate/serviceConfigItemById/:id							
GET		/climate/serviceConfigItemByServiceConfig/:serviceConfigId	
GET		/climate/serviceConfigItemByParamName/:param				
POST	/climate/addServiceConfigItem								
PUT		/climate/updateServiceConfigItem/id/:id						
